%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D1610201149&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=079b756e\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1610201149</a><br />\n<br />\nAlternative Lighting－鍾意貼近原著黑暗少少可以用呢隻, 少鮮艷色彩突出返暗色系<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1266710724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D1266710724&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=e8e82116\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1266710724</a><br />\n<br />\nLegendary Lore－介紹設定嘅Mod, 領主去到某啲地方或者打某啲特定角色會彈相關資料俾你了解, 幾啱鍾意睇Lore嘅玩家(得英文同殘體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1656114127\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D1656114127&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=4eef0be3\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1656114127</a><br />\n<br />\nReshade－呢個嚴格嚟講唔算Mod, 而係一個後期再加強畫質嘅Software, 有興趣可以跟下面條Link 安裝(P.S. 有可能導致Lag, 自問部腦有返咁上下就試下啦)<br />\n<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1902482257\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcommunity.com%2Fsharedfiles%2Ffiledetails%2F%3Fid%3D1902482257&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=1a725b5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1902482257</a><br />\n<br />\n以上都係官方版通用嘅戰役MOD, 鍾意Hardcore少少嘅可以自己發掘其他類似SFO嘅大改MOD"},{"pid":"53542eceeb6080dd024ffa15151f1d9248fc7150","tid":2490304,"uid":127148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"裝咗MOD同Reshade嘅靚Game shots<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/Rgz3hFysVkzPv0sxmJ/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=